common.name: VoiceStateStore
common.reason: To get members in a voice channel.

common.name: GuildActions
common.reason: To move members in a voice channel.

common.name: PermissionStore
common.reason: To check if the user has permission to move members in a voice channel.

default.MOVE_BULK_COMMAND_DESCRIPTION: Move members in a voice channel to another voice channel.
default.MOVE_BULK_CHANNEL_FROM_DESCRIPTION: The voice channel where the members to be moved are located.
default.MOVE_BULK_CHANNEL_TO_DESCRIPTION: The voice channel where the members will be moved.
default.MOVE_BULK_CHANNEL_NOT_FOUND: The voice channel you specified could not be found.
default.MOVE_BULK_PERMISSION_DENIED: You do not have permission to move members in one of the voice channels you specified.
default.MOVE_BULK_NO_MEMBERS: No members found in the voice channel you specified.
default.JOIN_VOICE_CHANNEL_NOT_FOUND: The voice channel you specified could not be found.
default.JOIN_VOICE_PERMISSION_DENIED: You do not have permission to join the voice channel you specified.

tr.MOVE_BULK_COMMAND_DESCRIPTION: Bir ses kanalındaki üyeleri başka bir ses kanalına taşır.
tr.MOVE_BULK_PERMISSION_DENIED: Belirttiğiniz ses kanallarından birinde üyeleri taşıma izniniz yok.
tr.JOIN_VOICE_PERMISSION_DENIED: Belirttiğiniz ses kanalına katılma izniniz yok.
